     F** UTLR75C **********************************************************
     F*  UTILITY- GET IAF FINAL GODDS PART FROM COMPONENT PART
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR75C' PLST1 ...
     F*                    PARM           $CPART 12
     F*                    PARM           $FPRT1 12
     F*                    PARM           $FPRT2 12
     F*                    PARM           $FPRT3 12
     F*                    PARM           $FPRT4 12
     F*                    PARM           $FPRT5 12
     F*   IN  $IPART 12A   IAF PART
     F*   OUT PLST1 ...
     F*       $FPRT1 12A   FINAL PART 1
     F*       $FPRT2 12A   FINAL PART 2
     F*       $FPRT3 12A   FINAL PART 3
     F*       $FPRT4 12A   FINAL PART 4
     F*       $FPRT5 12A   FINAL PART 5
     F******************************************************************
     FFCEPL01BIF  E           K        DISK
     F******************************************************************
     E                    PRT        50 12
     I            DS
     I                                        1  12 #SHIN
     I                                        1   5 #SHN1
